# ==========================================
# SDUI Blade Environment Configuration
# ==========================================
# The SDUI Blade core system purely orchestrates JSON payloads on the frontend.
# It is completely agnostic to your backend infrastructure.
# You can wire the UI endpoints to any Database (Postgres, MySQL, SQLite)
# and any ORM (Drizzle, Prisma, TypeORM). 
# (Note: We use Supabase/Postgres internally with Drizzle ORM)

# Example connection strings for your implementing application:
# DB_URL="postgres://user:pass@localhost:5432/dbname"
# DB_URL="mysql://user:pass@localhost:3306/dbname"
# ORM_PREFERENCE="drizzle"
